## Running it locally

If you want to run this on your own machine:

```bash
git clone https://github.com/ihtishamaliamir/ihtishamaliamir.github.io
cd ihtishamaliamir.github.io
bundle install
bundle exec jekyll serve
Then open http://localhost:4000 in your browser.

